@startuml yoshixmk_remarks

participant "Chrome Extension" as CE
participant "Deno Web Server" as Server
participant "FaunaDB" as DB
participant "GitPress Blog" as Blog

CE -> Server: POST /remarks (Create new remark)
Server -> DB: Execute GraphQL mutation
DB --> Server: Return created remark
Server --> CE: Confirm remark creation

CE -> Server: GET / (Request homepage)
Server -> DB: Query total remarks count
DB --> Server: Return count
Server -> DB: Query recent remarks
DB --> Server: Return recent remarks
Server --> CE: Render homepage with count and remarks

CE -> Server: GET /trip (Request travelogue)
Server -> Blog: Fetch RSS feed
Blog --> Server: Return blog posts
Server --> CE: Render travelogue page

CE -> Server: GET /quotes (Request quotes)
Server -> DB: Execute GraphQL query for quotes
DB --> Server: Return quotes
Server --> CE: Send quotes data

CE -> Server: POST /quotes (Create new quote)
Server -> DB: Execute GraphQL mutation
DB --> Server: Return created quote
Server --> CE: Confirm quote creation

@enduml